---
// Hero.astro — Updated with real LinkedIn data
---

<header id="top" class="hero wrap">

  <div class="hero-status reveal">
    <span class="dot-live" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    Open to freelance &amp; consulting · 2026
  </div>

  <h1 class="hero-title">
    <span class="line"><span>Fullstack</span></span>
    <span class="line"><span class="accent">Developer</span></span>
    <span class="line"><span class="outline">&amp; IT</span> <span>Manager</span></span>
    <span class="line"><span>Jakarta.</span></span>
  </h1>

  <p class="hero-sub reveal" data-d="2">
    Saya <strong>Isnaeni Hidayat</strong> — <strong>Fullstack Developer</strong> &amp; <strong>IT Manager</strong> berbasis di Jakarta.
    Lebih dari 10 tahun membangun sistem web end-to-end — dari arsitektur backend Laravel &amp; API sampai antarmuka Vue.js yang terasa mulus — untuk startup, korporasi, dan yayasan.
  </p>

  <div class="hero-meta">
    <div class="item reveal" data-d="2">
      <div class="k"><span data-count="10" data-suffix="+">10+</span></div>
      <div class="l">Years building</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item reveal" data-d="3">
      <div class="k"><span data-count="4" data-suffix=" yrs">4 yrs</span></div>
      <div class="l">Freelancing</div>
    </div>
    <div class="item reveal" data-d="4">
      <div class="k"><span data-count="7" data-suffix="">7</span></div>
      <div class="l">Companies served</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-actions reveal" data-d="3">
    <a href="#work" class="btn btn-primary" data-magnetic="0.3" id="hero-cta-work">
      View selected work <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
    </a>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-ghost" data-magnetic="0.3" id="hero-cta-contact">
      Get in touch
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- tech marquee — real stack -->
  <div class="marquee reveal" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="marquee-track">
      <span>Laravel</span><span>Vue.js</span><span>Node.js</span><span>MySQL</span><span>PostgreSQL</span><span>PHP</span><span>JavaScript</span><span>Odoo ERP</span><span>REST API</span><span>Docker</span><span>Linux</span><span>Git</span>
      <span>Laravel</span><span>Vue.js</span><span>Node.js</span><span>MySQL</span><span>PostgreSQL</span><span>PHP</span><span>JavaScript</span><span>Odoo ERP</span><span>REST API</span><span>Docker</span><span>Linux</span><span>Git</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-scroll" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="scroll-bar"></div>
    SCROLL
  </div>

</header>
